response.overview: The rebels gear up for battle against the ruthless forces of the Motherworld as unbreakable bonds are forged, heroes emerge — and legends are made.  The battle begins on a remote moon in "Chapter Two: Curse of Forgiveness," Zack Snyder's intense director's cut of his sci-fi saga.
response.tagline: Protect each other and show them no mercy!
